  m_Name: Clue 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::KeyItem
  guid: e11dcad1-28b3-4a4a-a5cc-66f913b47bbe
  itemName: Note #2
  description: "Boss,\r\n\r\nWe had to move further ahead than planned. One of the
    key pieces has been left deeper in the next section.\r\n\r\nIsaac and Alex are
    watching the area and keeping it secure. So far nothing\u2019s moved, but this
    place doesn\u2019t feel right.\r\n\r\nWe\u2019re keeping the pieces separated,
    just like you said. They\u2019re not getting put together.\r\n\r\nHurry.\r\n\n\nTold
    us to bust the key and stash the pieces in the sewer. One piece goes west, one
    goes east, last one northeast.\n\n\nDon't go lookin' for 'em. You don't wanna
    know."
  icon: {fileID: 7509403117698529453, guid: 945f2a5ccec718842a0f13fe94a2b967, type: 3}
  itemType: 1
